{"type": "article", "id": 4019, "title": "Earbud Wrap 耳机收纳器", "description": "", "date": "2014-12-02T08:18:45Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 8, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606052332522QSkeAGzwjfEHLPl.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t把多余的电缆线、耳机线卷曲放入圆盒子里进行收纳，就不会看起来很乱了,这就是 Dotz 的设计理念。这家来自巴黎的公司一直认为，最好的想法就是最简单的，正如这款 Earbud Wrap 。设计团队认为对于那些走在路上喜欢听歌的朋友来说，Earbud Wrap 是个不错的选择，它的夹式设计可以保持耳机在使用与非使用状态时都与这个收纳器绑在一起，你可以将它夹于衬衫、包袋以及夹克等任何你认为可以夹的地方。定价 4.99 美元，<a href=\"http://www.dotzshop.com/index.php/cord-management-products/ear-bud-wraps/earbud-wrap.html\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<iframe height=\"498\" width=\"640\" src=\"http://player.youku.com/embed/XODM5NTQzMDg0\" frameborder=\"0\">\r\n</iframe>\r\n<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233250nOTkg2ejtp4FY8af.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233251DCGRZIgWNYPKm6cb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233251oNBHgTrfYSvdXkpD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}